{"tid":1707754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日集合時間地點！","createTime":"2019-11-11T11:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T11:36:15.000Z","uid":67645,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f39a154d27ee269a9e7084eeac7c542a6e6d224e","tid":1707754,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"今日咁多手足比狗咬，好大原因係因為聚唔到人，無哨兵同和理非做阻隔，手足一做野就好易被咬！<br />\n<br />\n既然講定時間地點會比啲狗佈防，我建議聽日集合地點係黨鐵月台，扮返工嘅人，未夠鐘就遊下車河，就算啲狗企哂入地鐵都無辦法分到你係返工定係示威！<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位覺得可行嘅就再開post討論確實時間，地點可以聽朝大家都係黨鐵車廂再公佈，確保早到嘅手足都唔洗企係條街等人拉！"},{"pid":"d62d09e4f912d9ee9888eda67e5619e4dbcfa1b4","tid":1707754,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2df77cab8b81e0274c3d30127c5f1a0782c8d23","tid":1707754,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:18:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"230b87125573fe779b6e858a0d8e95b524e528c1","tid":1707754,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:18:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f187c75883ecef636431a0b69fa910552adebb9","tid":1707754,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"599656101fd84bc1dce5d98e259db4b3974f9e00","tid":1707754,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef2d72dfc53de45d59f4134c0b666e9a10e0406d","tid":1707754,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04037e693121031ebd688fe6b41f8ac9e56eee57","tid":1707754,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"263ddd8e54e629faf440a404e11a1bccdff66787","tid":1707754,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:24:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dcc51f4482e78bd2d367286575aa8e483245354","tid":1707754,"uid":67645,"like